Exercise: Delcaring a DTD for our BusinessCard XML file:

- Inline DTD can be included using the following code:

<!DOCTYPE BusinessCard [

<!ELEMENT BusinessCard (Name, phone+, email?)>
<!ELEMENT Name (#PCDATA)>

<!ELEMENT phone (#PCDATA)>
<!ATTLIST phone type (mobile | fax | work | home) #REQUIRED>

<!ELEMENT email (#PCDATA)>

]>

Example: 15-Declaring-internal-DTD project
